name: babi guling selingsing " men wima "
address: F464+CHR, Jl. Garuda Jl. Selingsing, Pangkung Karung, Kec. Kerambitan, Kabupaten Tabanan, Bali 82111, Indonesia
review 1:
commonly the taste of cycling pig between tabanan and denpasar is totally diferent , could  be on the seasoning.
the taste of the soup in here is not fresh anymore bcoz the meat looks come from the remaining fried meat, cud be the day b4.
review 2: Great Babi guling. If you a baby guling lover, you have to try. The Buh Wina.
review 3: The balinese food (babi guling) is very very tasty but the price is a little bit expensive and the place is not comfortable
review 4: babi guling/suckling pig. with local taste...so yummy... #bqli #food #traditional

name: Babi Guling Men Rebo
address: Br. Selingsing,, F443+MQM, Pangkung Karung, Kerambitan, Tabanan Regency, Bali 82111, Indonesia
review 1: The food is simple but authentic. Taste great. I got amazing crunchy skin, lucky me. They serve with glove on, that's a point today for non-local customers. Not sure, but the rice is bit hard.
review 2: Taste good, if u compare with other babi guling around tabanan this one is the best taste, i rate 5 star for the taste. Make sure come early for the first serve. Open only in Wednesday and friday but make sure open in Wednesday. No photo for this the queue for the food so crazy.
review 3: Amazing pork sate and it is non halal just a reminder
